== Related Articles == * {{ill|Japanese administrative system|ja|日本の官制|1=Japanese administrative system|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese administrative system|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese administrative system|qq=}} * {{ill|Heian-kyō|ja|平安京|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heian-kyō|qq=}} * {{ill|Kebishō|ja|検非違使|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kebishō|qq=}}
