q=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shoshōi|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Initial Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 少初位}}) ** '''Bōchō''' (坊長): Subordinate neighborhood official * Support staff included '''Shishō''' (clerks), '''Shokushō''' (operational staff), and laborers.
